45:31.829 --> 45:38.135 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Early in his new
memoir, Elvis Costello writes
about his father, Ross McManus,

45:38.135 --> 45:42.139 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
