as a bebop jazz musician.

45:42.139 --> 45:46.344 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELVIS COSTELLO, Musician: I have
a clipping that I reproduce in
the book where it says,

45:46.344 --> 45:50.781 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the Ross McManus Quintet direct
from their engagements in Paris
and London. And at that

45:50.781 --> 45:51.916 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
