twin 8-year-old sons. And he
brings the story full circle

51:32.890 --> 51:36.093 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
with the death of his
father four years ago.

51:36.093 --> 51:41.332 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELVIS COSTELLO: His passing was
poignant, in the way that I
related it, because he had

51:41.332 --> 51:46.403 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
been a very vivid personality,
and the nature of his demise was
through Parkinson's and

51:46.403 --> 51:51.108 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
