that, erasing his senses little
by little, of which music

51:51.108 --> 51:55.546 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
was about the last companion,
which was very, very moving for
me.

51:55.546 --> 51:58.816 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. Was that
part of the impetus, though, for
you to write this book?

51:58.816 --> 52:02.786 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELVIS COSTELLO: Well, I think
the impetus to get it finished
in a form that you now

52:02.786 --> 52:03.520 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
see it.

52:03.520 --> 52:05.489 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes.

52:05.489 --> 52:07.958 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ELVIS COSTELLO: Certainly,
because I was able to talk with
him with clarity in the -- as

52:07.958 --> 52:10.260 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
