know, because I am the last,
best witness.

52:30.514 --> 52:32.983 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right,
"Unfaithful Music and
Disappearing Ink."

52:32.983 --> 52:33.951 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Elvis Costello, thank you.

